Package org.apache.jackrabbit.spi.commons.query

Class PropertyFunctionQueryNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.jackrabbit.spi.commons.query.QueryNode
      • org.apache.jackrabbit.spi.commons.query.PropertyFunctionQueryNode
  • public class PropertyFunctionQueryNode
extends QueryNode
    PropertyFunctionQueryNode allows to place function calls on properties in a query. Supported function names are:
    • upper-case as specified in fn:upper-case()
    • lower-case as specified in fn:lower-case()

    • Field Summary
